trans-unit.source: Describes an object that wraps a pair of values.
For more information, see [pair (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3326b4d9-a52a-49e5-8103-9aa5e8b352de).
Type of the first value in the pair.
Type of the second value in the pair.

Constructs a new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object with default values for <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.first"></xref> and <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.second"></xref>.
For more information, see [pair::pair (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188035f3-bd37-4b46-96dd-5ceb9a16df79).
Constructs a new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object from an existing <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair`2"></xref> object.
For more information, see [pair::pair (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188035f3-bd37-4b46-96dd-5ceb9a16df79).
The <xref href="System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair`2"></xref> object to be copied into the new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object.
Constructs a new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object and assigns its first value to the specified value.
For more information, see [pair::pair (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188035f3-bd37-4b46-96dd-5ceb9a16df79).
The value to store in <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.first"></xref>.
The <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.second"></xref> value is assigned the default value for its type.
Constructs a new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object with the two values specified.
For more information, see [pair::pair (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188035f3-bd37-4b46-96dd-5ceb9a16df79).
The value to store in <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.first"></xref>.
The value to store in <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2.second"></xref>.
Determines if two <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> objects are equal.
For more information, see [operator== (pair) (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2b4879a1-f326-4fb3-b113-bd8d457f9802).
The <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object to compare with the current <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object.
`true` if the two <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> objects are equal; otherwise, `false`.
The first wrapped value of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object.
For more information, see [pair::first (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/0dd2278f-adf9-46df-8ac8-7e8e1a2ef52e).
The second wrapped value of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.GenericPair`2"></xref> object.
For more information, see [pair::second (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f30d3d1f-c7be-45d2-92ff-6861b96a92ff).
